OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with further showers,
OL,7,Fthese focused across the north. Some
OL,8,Fovernight clear spells developing,
OL,9,Fchiefly towards the southern end of
OL,10,FGreat Glen where showers will largely
OL,11,Fdie out.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FMost enjoying a dry day with
OL,14,Fgood sunny spells and light winds,
OL,15,Fwith the Great Glen best favoured.
OL,16,FHowever, some early light showers
OL,17,Fpossible, chiefly in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
